-- Telecom Italia's Chief Bernabe Says Fixed, Mobile Clients `Coming Back'
-- Chiara Remondini
-- 2010-09-20T11:13:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/telecom-italia-s-chief-bernabe-says-fixed-mobile-clients-coming-back-.html

          
          
             Telecom Italia SpA doesn’t foresee
changes to its current business plan, Chief Executive Officer
Franco Bernabe told reporters in Milan today.  
 Fixed and mobile clients are “coming back to the
company,” Bernabe said. Telecom Italia is focused on cutting
debt and on conditions for growth, the CEO said.  
          
          


  


        